---
// PricingTable.astro — Pricing page, strictly based on HTML reference
---

<!-- ===== Hero ===== -->
<header class="pricing-hero">
  <div class="pricing-hero__inner">
    <h1 class="pricing-hero__title">
      Read Smarter, <span class="pricing-hero__accent">Not Just Later.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="pricing-hero__sub">
      Save Forever, Learn faster. Your intelligent library for high efficiency and deep undersatanding.
    </p>

    <!-- Promo Banner -->
    <a class="pricing-promo" href="https://r.slax.com/login">
      <span aria-hidden="true">🎉</span>
      Join today and get 1 Month of Pro Free
    </a>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ===== Pricing Table ===== -->
<section class="pricing-wrap">
  <div class="pricing-table-scroll">
    <table class="pricing-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <!-- Col 1: label -->
          <th class="pt-label-col">
            <h2 class="pt-section-title">Pricing Plans</h2>
          </th>

          <!-- Col 2: Free -->
          <th class="pt-plan-col">
            <div class="pt-plan">
              <h3 class="pt-plan__name">Free</h3>
              <div class="pt-plan__price">
                <span class="pt-plan__amount">$0</span>
                <span class="pt-plan__period">/ Month</span>
              </div>
              <p class="pt-plan__desc">
                Unlimited bookmarks &amp; backup forever — join now before limits apply!
              </p>
              <a class="pt-plan__btn" href="https://r.slax.com/login">Start Free</a>
            </div>
          </th>

          <!-- Col 3: Pro Reader -->
          <th class="pt-plan-col pt-plan-col--pro">
            <div class="pt-plan">
              <h3 class="pt-plan__name pt-plan__name--pro">Pro Reader</h3>
              <div class="pt-plan__price">
                <span class="pt-plan__amount">$5.99</span>
                <span class="pt-plan__period">/ Month</span>
                <span class="pt-plan__strike">($9.99)</span>
              </div>
              <p class="pt-plan__desc">
                Unleash your reading superpowers with integrated AI analysis.
              </p>
              <a class="pt-plan__btn pt-plan__btn--pro" href="https://r.slax.com/login">
                Try 1 Month Free
              </a>
            </div>
          </th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>

        <!-- ── Free + Pro rows ── -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Save Unlimited Articles</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Permanent Snapshots (no broken links)</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Unlimited Highlights &amp; Comments</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Full-Text Search</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Sync Across All Devices</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Share Articles &amp; Join Discussions</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Open Source &amp; Privacy-First</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Create &amp; Manage Tags</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
          <td class="pt-check">✓</td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── AI / Pro-only rows ── -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Smart AI Auto-Tagging</td>
          <td class="pt-cross">✕</td>
          <td class="pt-ai">
            <span class="pt-ai-badge">AI</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Instant AI Summaries</td>
          <td class="pt-cross">✕</td>
          <td class="pt-ai">
            <span class="pt-ai-badge">AI</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">Interactive AI Outlines</td>
          <td class="pt-cross">✕</td>
          <td class="pt-ai">
            <span class="pt-ai-badge">AI</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="pt-feat">AI Chatbot — Ask Your Library Anything</td>
          <td class="pt-cross">✕</td>
          <td class="pt-ai">
            <span class="pt-ai-badge">AI</span>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
<section class="pricing-faq">
  <div class="pricing-faq__inner">
    <h2 class="pricing-faq__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <details class="faq-item" open>
      <summary class="faq-item__q">Is the Free plan really free forever?</summary>
      <p class="faq-item__a">
        Yes — for early users. We're offering unlimited bookmarks and permanent backups at no cost
        while we're in early access. Lock in free usage now before limits apply.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-item__q">Will Slax Reader really save me hours of reading every week?</summary>
      <p class="faq-item__a">
        That's what it's built for. Clickable AI outlines let you navigate long articles without
        reading every word. Auto-tagging handles the organizing, so you can just read.
        <a href="/reader/blog/a-smarter-more-efficient-ai-powered-way-to-save-and-read-forever" class="faq-item__link">Full Visual Tour →</a>
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-item__q">Can I cancel my Pro subscription anytime?</summary>
      <p class="faq-item__a">
        Absolutely. Cancel any time from your account settings with no penalties. Your saved
        articles and highlights remain accessible on the Free plan.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-item__q">How does the 1 Month Free trial work?</summary>
      <p class="faq-item__a">
        <a href="https://r.slax.com/login" class="faq-item__link">Sign in</a> and start your trial — no credit card required. After 30 days you'll be
        asked if you'd like to continue with Pro at $5.99 / month (regular price $9.99).
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
<section class="pricing-cta">
  <div class="pricing-cta__inner">
    <h2 class="pricing-cta__title">Start Your Intelligent Reading Journey Today</h2>
    <p class="pricing-cta__sub">Read smarter, learn faster, remember more</p>
    <a class="pricing-cta__btn" href="https://r.slax.com/login">
      <span>Get Started — It's Free</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ── Hero ── */
  .pricing-hero {
    padding: 80px 0 72px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fffc 0%, #e6fff3 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-hero__inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .pricing-hero__title {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #1f1f1f;
  }

  .pricing-hero__accent {
    color: #16b998;
  }

  .pricing-hero__sub {
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333333;
  }

  /* ── Promo Banner ── */
  .pricing-promo {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #16b998 0%, #5edda8 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pricing-promo:hover {
    opacity: 0.88;
  }

  /* ── Table Wrapper ── */
  .pricing-wrap {
    padding: 60px 0 80px;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .pricing-table-scroll {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  /* ── Table ── */
  .pricing-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .pricing-table thead tr {
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .pricing-table th,
  .pricing-table td {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f5;
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .pricing-table tbody tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* Label column */
  .pt-label-col {
    width: 46%;
  }

  .pt-section-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f1f1f;
  }

  /* Plan columns */
  .pt-plan-col {
    width: 27%;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .pt-plan-col--pro {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0fdf8 0%, #ffffff 100%);
  }

  .pt-plan__name {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #1f1f1f;
  }

  .pt-plan__name--pro {
    color: #16b998;
  }

  .pt-plan__price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .pt-plan__amount {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1f1f1f;
  }

  .pt-plan__period {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #666666;
  }

  .pt-plan__strike {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #999999;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .pt-plan__desc {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #555555;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .pt-plan__btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #f0f0f0;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pt-plan__btn:hover {
    background: #e0e0e0;
  }

  .pt-plan__btn--pro {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25d4b0 0%, #1cb0b5 50%, #16b998 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .pt-plan__btn--pro:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Feature rows */
  .pt-feat {
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    color: #333333;
  }

  .pt-check {
    text-align: center;
    color: #16b998;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .pt-cross {
    text-align: center;
    color: #cccccc;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .pt-ai {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pt-ai-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #16b998 0%, #5edda8 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ── FAQ ── */
  .pricing-faq {
    padding: 60px 0 80px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .pricing-faq__inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .pricing-faq__title {
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-item__q {
    display: block;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .faq-item__q::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item__q::after {
    content: '+';
    float: right;
    color: #16b998;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .faq-item__q::after {
    content: '−';
  }

  .faq-item__a {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 20px 18px;
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555555;
  }

  .faq-item__link {
    color: #16b998;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .faq-item__link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .pricing-cta {
    padding: 68px 0 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2eb396 0%, #5edda8 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-cta__inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .pricing-cta__title {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .pricing-cta__sub {
    margin: 0 0 36px;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .pricing-cta__btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    min-height: 56px;
    padding: 0 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pricing-cta__btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
  }
</style>

